uld you mind to become a whistleblower like our article’s main role? Why?<br />2.How can we define whistleblower? Justice warrior or black sheep or…….?<br />3.Do you think we should protect whistleblowers? Why? How?<br />4.Do you agree the more whistleblowers the less corruption?<br />5.Widely speaking, whistleblower, include 檢舉魔人. What do you think of this career?<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=872">Shuman</a> — Sat Oct 16, 2021 8:59 pm</p><hr />
